{"tid":2232103,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個綺夢情節","createTime":"2020-10-06T07:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T07:12:56.000Z","uid":65433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2c805b6233c28072b310039a57864db7d242e76c","tid":2232103,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T07:09:01.000Z","msg":"大學時期有四個幾friend嘅女仔，講唔上靚但都未稱得上樣衰，四個分別係5/5/6/6.5分咁上下<br />\n咁多年來都講唔上對佢哋有好大興趣，亦都已經好多年無見<br />\n無啦啦尋晚發夢四個同我一齊除晒衫浸溫泉<br />\n浸浸下唔小心埃咗埋去其中一個5分度<br />\n佢又無避，大家都feel到對方著咗火<br />\n其餘三個好興奮咁笑我哋<br />\n跟住...<br />\n<br />\n...跟住就醒咗<br />\n緊住火咁開電腦，搵返張陳年舊相嚟J<br />\nJ完之後又唔覺得心底入面對佢有咩感情<br />\n總之成件事好無厘頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4cf9b8f06438c3c902b13c33d90689f1fcb336","tid":2232103,"uid":136416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T07:10:58.000Z","msg":"睇標題諗住入黎講吳君如格勒底食龍蝦<br />\n點知真係綺夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span class=\"x-small\">［超突發］德國政府官方聯署中文版 夠數德國會就要討論制裁中國<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2231827\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2231827</a> 大家快d簽<br />\n[獻給林夕] 「兒歌」 巴絲打可唔可幫手推俾夕爺聽 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2231822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2231822</a></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c1f61b0001ca7345cba6bbd327dc7b6ed016f600","tid":2232103,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T07:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://prd-image-masters.caravan-stories.com.tw/c/u=0,a=0,r=auto,w=1500,sig=1.9EaDVEFomOWcWWB25ndkjPTWzYpPnIQf-w0w1phsJb0=/caravan-stories/masters/production-tw/attachments/515ce9c6c4e8bd9bdc74aad39ac09f36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprd-image-masters.caravan-stories.com.tw%2Fc%2Fu%3D0%2Ca%3D0%2Cr%3Dauto%2Cw%3D1500%2Csig%3D1.9EaDVEFomOWcWWB25ndkjPTWzYpPnIQf-w0w1phsJb0%3D%2Fcaravan-stories%2Fmasters%2Fproduction-tw%2Fattachments%2F515ce9c6c